Title : Worm syrup
Text : {{Unsourced|date=April 2014}}
'''Worm syrup''' was a [[patent medicine]] sold in glass bottles. The concoctions were intended to get rid of parasitic worms. Brands included DeWitt's Worm Syrup, Kopp's Electric Worm SyrupBumstead's Worm Syrup, and Fahrney Inf'allibel Worm Syrup. Worm syrups are also sold for animals. Modern worm syrups are also sold.

